{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":7,"day":26}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"民兵兄弟（古巴）","authors":["埃米略·达尔科尔"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们民兵是兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家有着一个共同的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了我们的民族。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要永远献出自己的主命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个非常美丽的早晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定会来到我们的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们将坚持不懈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行勇敢的斗争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们祖国的敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心只想进行剥削，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果他们胆敢动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们很快会遭到灭亡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"企图破坏和平的家伙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在我们的土地上出现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们绝对不能放松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取荣誉和自由的步枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们希望我们的子女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在和平中成长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望古巴美丽的星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在空中闪耀着崇高的亮光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（金仁伯译自古巴《革命报》）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}